1
00:00:04,839 --> 00:00:05,547
<b>[IMORI] Why, Moegi?</b>

2
00:00:07,549 --> 00:00:10,594
<b>[MOEGI] I need you
on the other squad, that's why.</b>

3
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:12,680
<b>But--</b>

4
00:00:12,721 --> 00:00:13,973
<b>[MOEGI] But?</b>

5
00:00:15,724 --> 00:00:17,518
<b>But what?
- Nothing.</b>

6
00:00:17,559 --> 00:00:18,519
<b>She'll go.</b>

7
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:19,812
<b>Right?</b>

8
00:00:21,229 --> 00:00:22,230
<b>Yeah.</b>

9
00:00:22,272 --> 00:00:23,524
<b>Sorry.</b>

10
00:00:25,275 --> 00:00:27,653
<b>[whimsical music]</b>

11
00:00:27,695 --> 00:00:34,994
<b>♪ ♪</b>

12
00:01:01,395 --> 00:01:02,604
<b>No one here.</b>

13
00:01:02,646 --> 00:01:03,898
<b>Yeah.</b>

14
00:01:09,528 --> 00:01:11,238
<b>[rustle, gasps]</b>

15
00:01:13,448 --> 00:01:15,116
<b>[rustling]</b>

16
00:01:15,868 --> 00:01:18,077
<b>[hollow ringing]</b>

17
00:01:18,829 --> 00:01:21,248
<b>[playing scales]</b>

18
00:01:21,289 --> 00:01:23,000
<b>[groans]</b>

19
00:01:23,751 --> 00:01:24,877
<b>Stupid bunny.</b>

20
00:01:24,919 --> 00:01:27,421
<b>Hey, Kozue, look
at what I found.</b>

21
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,052
<b>Kozue?</b>

22
00:01:35,303 --> 00:01:36,555
<b>Nishida?</b>

23
00:01:44,063 --> 00:01:45,313
<b>Guys?</b>

24
00:01:49,651 --> 00:01:51,110
<b>Where'd you all go?</b>

25
00:01:52,821 --> 00:01:53,948
<b>Come on.</b>

26
00:01:53,989 --> 00:01:55,198
<b>This isn't funny.</b>

27
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:57,910
<b>[rustling]</b>

28
00:01:59,078 --> 00:02:00,746
<b>[groans]</b>

29
00:02:01,496 --> 00:02:02,998
<b>[grunts, static]</b>

30
00:02:04,165 --> 00:02:07,252
<b>[hysterical laughing]</b>

31
00:02:09,838 --> 00:02:11,924
<b>What the hell are
they doing to her?</b>

32
00:02:14,509 --> 00:02:15,469
<b>Interrogating.</b>

33
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,762
<b>Huh?</b>

34
00:02:16,804 --> 00:02:18,639
<b>So, where's your team
hiding your weapons?</b>

35
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:22,059
<b>[YUKI] I mean, we were told
not to use violence, so.</b>

36
00:02:22,101 --> 00:02:23,644
<b>I don't--</b>

37
00:02:23,685 --> 00:02:27,606
<b>She'd talk quicker if they
broke a few of her fingers.</b>

38
00:02:27,648 --> 00:02:31,735
<b>With a team as big as ours is,
that would cause problems.</b>

39
00:02:31,777 --> 00:02:33,445
<b>Hm?</b>

40
00:02:33,487 --> 00:02:35,196
<b>It's about morals.</b>

41
00:02:35,238 --> 00:02:38,325
<b>Without them, there's no way we
can keep this group together.</b>

42
00:02:38,366 --> 00:02:41,829
<b>And Hakushi put me here
to keep these newbies in line.</b>

43
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,122
<b>Huh.</b>

44
00:02:44,623 --> 00:02:46,667
<b>[YUKI]
She says her name's Kushieda,</b>

45
00:02:46,708 --> 00:02:48,710
<b>and there's about 30
on her team.</b>

46
00:02:48,752 --> 00:02:50,337
<b>Their leader's
called Moegi,</b>

47
00:02:50,378 --> 00:02:52,089
<b>and she's using fear
and intimidation</b>

48
00:02:52,131 --> 00:02:54,215
<b>to keep everyone in line.</b>

49
00:02:54,257 --> 00:02:55,676
<b>[SUMIYAKA] Yikes.</b>

50
00:02:55,717 --> 00:02:58,804
<b>I guess our team's the better
one to be on, then.</b>

51
00:02:58,846 --> 00:03:00,055
<b>Oh, yeah.</b>

52
00:03:00,097 --> 00:03:01,598
<b>Here it comes.</b>

53
00:03:02,724 --> 00:03:04,018
<b>Tickle!</b>

54
00:03:04,059 --> 00:03:05,393
<b>Tickle, tickle,
tickle, tickle, tickle!</b>

55
00:03:05,435 --> 00:03:06,145
<b>Hee hee!</b>

56
00:03:07,395 --> 00:03:10,816
<b>Looks like playing instead
of, you know, torturing.</b>

57
00:03:10,858 --> 00:03:13,527
<b>And weirdly enough,
it gets results.</b>

58
00:03:13,568 --> 00:03:16,738
<b>Like, have you ever been
tickled by that many people?</b>

59
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:18,073
<b>Oh, hell no.</b>

60
00:03:18,115 --> 00:03:19,366
<b>Never.</b>

61
00:03:20,701 --> 00:03:23,704
<b>Tell us where
your weapons are.</b>

62
00:03:23,745 --> 00:03:24,913
<b>Tickle!</b>

63
00:03:24,955 --> 00:03:29,334
<b>Hey! [laughter] Don't.</b>

64
00:03:29,376 --> 00:03:31,545
<b>[grunts, pants]</b>

65
00:03:32,295 --> 00:03:33,338
<b>Oh, yeah.</b>

66
00:03:33,380 --> 00:03:35,132
<b>I'm down with this technique.</b>

67
00:03:36,675 --> 00:03:38,177
<b>What?</b>

68
00:03:38,217 --> 00:03:39,720
<b>[grunts]</b>

69
00:03:39,761 --> 00:03:40,721
<b>Nice try.</b>

70
00:03:40,762 --> 00:03:41,722
<b>Don't!</b>

71
00:03:41,763 --> 00:03:45,017
<b>[laughter]</b>

72
00:03:46,768 --> 00:03:47,728
<b>Huh?</b>

73
00:03:47,769 --> 00:03:49,021
<b>Hm?</b>

74
00:03:51,773 --> 00:03:55,027
<b>[panting, gasping]</b>

75
00:03:56,153 --> 00:03:57,404
<b>Sheesh.</b>

76
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:02,034
<b>What's your problem?</b>

77
00:04:03,284 --> 00:04:06,205
<b>[somber music]</b>

78
00:04:06,245 --> 00:04:13,503
<b>♪ ♪</b>

79
00:04:14,713 --> 00:04:18,466
<b>My next game,
I hit the wall of 30.</b>

80
00:04:19,634 --> 00:04:21,302
<b>[sighs]</b>

81
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:24,263
<b>Oh, come on.</b>

82
00:04:24,305 --> 00:04:26,600
<b>You don't believe
it's a curse, do you?</b>

83
00:04:27,851 --> 00:04:30,645
<b>I didn't think stuff
like that bothered you.</b>

84
00:04:30,687 --> 00:04:32,480
<b>It's cute.</b>

85
00:04:32,522 --> 00:04:36,818
<b>♪ ♪</b>

86
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:39,071
<b>[groans]</b>

87
00:04:41,198 --> 00:04:43,742
<b>I'm gonna hug you a bit longer.</b>

88
00:04:44,868 --> 00:04:48,287
<b>♪ ♪</b>

89
00:04:48,329 --> 00:04:51,458
<b>[footsteps falling, panting]</b>

90
00:04:52,209 --> 00:04:54,419
<b>Hey, stop!</b>

91
00:05:02,261 --> 00:05:03,511
<b>Huh?</b>

92
00:05:13,272 --> 00:05:15,023
<b>[hollow ringing]</b>

93
00:05:15,774 --> 00:05:18,277
<b>[playing scales]</b>

94
00:05:18,317 --> 00:05:20,279
<b>[yelps, grunts]</b>

95
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:22,030
<b>[scoffs]</b>

96
00:05:22,739 --> 00:05:24,992
<b>[whimpers]</b>

97
00:05:27,244 --> 00:05:28,703
<b>[chuckles]</b>

98
00:05:28,745 --> 00:05:30,247
<b>[gasps, gunshots]</b>

99
00:05:30,289 --> 00:05:31,999
<b>[frantic music]</b>

100
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,250
<b>Damn it!</b>

101
00:05:34,417 --> 00:05:41,758
<b>♪ ♪</b>

102
00:05:45,512 --> 00:05:46,847
<b>[grunts]</b>

103
00:05:46,888 --> 00:05:48,307
<b>[laughs]</b>

104
00:05:48,347 --> 00:05:51,226
<b>[panting, grunting]</b>

105
00:05:51,268 --> 00:05:55,689
<b>♪ ♪</b>

106
00:05:55,730 --> 00:05:57,398
<b>[struggling]</b>

107
00:05:57,440 --> 00:06:04,739
<b>♪ ♪</b>

108
00:06:09,036 --> 00:06:11,872
<b>[screams]</b>

109
00:06:11,913 --> 00:06:15,416
<b>♪ ♪</b>

110
00:06:15,458 --> 00:06:16,918
<b>[gunshot pops, grunts]</b>

111
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:19,213
<b>[casing clatters]</b>

112
00:06:23,466 --> 00:06:26,220
<b>[panting]</b>

113
00:06:28,471 --> 00:06:30,724
<b>[grunts, thuds]</b>

114
00:06:38,148 --> 00:06:40,567
<b>[static]</b>

115
00:06:41,818 --> 00:06:44,529
<b>[footsteps echoing]</b>

116
00:06:47,241 --> 00:06:49,993
<b>[MOEGI] Thanks
for saving my life.</b>

117
00:06:52,537 --> 00:06:54,622
<b>[playing scales]</b>

118
00:06:54,664 --> 00:06:55,665
<b>[AIRI] Of course.</b>

119
00:06:55,707 --> 00:06:56,958
<b>We're teammates.</b>

120
00:06:58,543 --> 00:06:59,878
<b>[MOEGI sighs]</b>

121
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:03,173
<b>I know, but thanks anyway.</b>

122
00:07:05,884 --> 00:07:07,386
<b>[playing scales]</b>

123
00:07:07,426 --> 00:07:11,098
<b>[static]</b>

124
00:07:12,849 --> 00:07:15,269
<b>[KANON] [gasping]</b>

125
00:07:15,310 --> 00:07:17,854
<b>[RECORDING] The tutorial
stage is over.</b>

126
00:07:17,896 --> 00:07:22,943
<b>Go forth and figure out
the rest for yourselves.</b>

127
00:07:22,984 --> 00:07:24,319
<b>The tutorial stage is--</b>

128
00:07:24,361 --> 00:07:26,029
<b>Hey, quit doing that.</b>

129
00:07:26,071 --> 00:07:29,699
<b>[RECORDING] Go forth and figure
out the rest for yourselves.</b>

130
00:07:33,536 --> 00:07:35,122
<b>The tutorial stage is over.</b>

131
00:07:35,163 --> 00:07:36,539
<b>I said quit doing that.</b>

132
00:07:37,707 --> 00:07:39,084
<b>What the heck's wrong with you?</b>

133
00:07:39,126 --> 00:07:40,501
<b>[curtain flutters]</b>

134
00:07:40,543 --> 00:07:42,296
<b>[startles, gasps]</b>

135
00:07:43,255 --> 00:07:45,506
<b>We-- we went out,
like you ordered.</b>

136
00:07:45,548 --> 00:07:48,593
<b>But our squad was
killed, and, like--</b>

137
00:07:48,635 --> 00:07:50,553
<b>there was nowhere else to go.</b>

138
00:07:50,595 --> 00:07:53,348
<b>[stammers] I didn't
run away, I swear.</b>

139
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:54,933
<b>[RECORDING] --stage is over.</b>

140
00:07:55,434 --> 00:07:56,435
<b>Go forth--</b>

141
00:07:56,475 --> 00:07:57,936
<b>[MOEGI] I'm not mad.</b>

142
00:07:57,978 --> 00:07:59,229
<b>I ran away, too.</b>

143
00:07:59,271 --> 00:08:00,521
<b>Huh?</b>

144
00:08:02,232 --> 00:08:03,233
<b>You did?</b>

145
00:08:03,275 --> 00:08:04,483
<b>What happened out there?</b>

146
00:08:04,525 --> 00:08:05,735
<b>You're OK?</b>

147
00:08:05,777 --> 00:08:07,279
<b>[RECORDING] The tutorial
stage is over.</b>

148
00:08:07,321 --> 00:08:08,947
<b>Are you hurt?</b>

149
00:08:08,989 --> 00:08:11,283
<b>[RECORDING] Go forth and figure
out the rest for yourself.</b>

150
00:08:11,325 --> 00:08:12,284
<b>It's OK.</b>

151
00:08:12,326 --> 00:08:13,534
<b>Really.</b>

152
00:08:14,828 --> 00:08:16,495
<b>How many Stumps
are still alive?</b>

153
00:08:16,537 --> 00:08:19,958
<b>[RECORDING] Go forth and figure
out the rest for yourself.</b>

154
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,584
<b>I don't know.</b>

155
00:08:21,626 --> 00:08:23,544
<b>[RECORDING] The tutorial
stage is over.</b>

156
00:08:23,586 --> 00:08:24,671
<b>Go forth--</b>

157
00:08:24,712 --> 00:08:27,132
<b>And what if
Team Bunny finds us?</b>

158
00:08:30,135 --> 00:08:32,220
<b>I don't know.</b>

159
00:08:32,262 --> 00:08:34,764
<b>[RECORDING] The tutorial
stage is over.</b>

160
00:08:34,806 --> 00:08:39,227
<b>Go forth and figure out
the rest for yourselves.</b>

161
00:08:39,269 --> 00:08:41,896
<b>[floor creaks]</b>

162
00:08:42,647 --> 00:08:44,774
<b>[groans]</b>

163
00:08:45,524 --> 00:08:47,235
<b>[clacks]</b>

164
00:08:49,404 --> 00:08:52,991
<b>The tutorial stage is over.</b>

165
00:08:53,033 --> 00:08:57,162
<b>Go forth and figure out
the rest for yourselves.</b>

166
00:08:59,373 --> 00:09:00,790
<b>[gunshot pops]</b>

167
00:09:00,832 --> 00:09:03,668
<b>[somber music]</b>

168
00:09:03,710 --> 00:09:10,467
<b>♪ ♪</b>

169
00:09:10,509 --> 00:09:15,472
<b>[MOEGI] The night hawk
is an ugly, ugly bird.</b>

170
00:09:15,514 --> 00:09:20,935
<b>It has splotches like flecks
of miso all over its face.</b>

171
00:09:20,977 --> 00:09:28,235
<b>♪ ♪</b>

172
00:09:34,366 --> 00:09:35,616
<b>Uh.</b>

173
00:09:37,327 --> 00:09:38,577
<b>Huh?</b>

174
00:09:39,829 --> 00:09:41,206
<b>[gasps]</b>

175
00:09:41,248 --> 00:09:47,670
<b>♪ ♪</b>

176
00:09:47,712 --> 00:09:48,963
<b>Hm.</b>

177
00:09:50,131 --> 00:09:57,472
<b>♪ ♪</b>

178
00:09:59,682 --> 00:10:01,518
<b>[KYARA] Thanks for waiting.</b>

179
00:10:05,439 --> 00:10:09,776
<b>Y-- you are so cool,
the way you killed her,</b>

180
00:10:09,817 --> 00:10:11,403
<b>like it was nothing.</b>

181
00:10:13,488 --> 00:10:16,032
<b>Please make me your student.</b>

182
00:10:16,074 --> 00:10:18,826
<b>[whimsical music]</b>

183
00:10:18,868 --> 00:10:23,081
<b>♪ ♪</b>

184
00:10:23,123 --> 00:10:24,999
<b>[KYARA] Do you like animals?</b>

185
00:10:27,668 --> 00:10:29,796
<b>Like dogs and cats?</b>

186
00:10:32,215 --> 00:10:36,136
<b>I don't hate them, I guess.</b>

187
00:10:37,678 --> 00:10:39,764
<b>[KYARA] Do you like
people who keep pets?</b>

188
00:10:39,806 --> 00:10:41,057
<b>Uh.</b>

189
00:10:42,100 --> 00:10:44,894
<b>♪ ♪</b>

190
00:10:44,936 --> 00:10:49,774
<b>I-- I don't like how
superior they think</b>

191
00:10:49,816 --> 00:10:53,111
<b>they are to, like, animals.</b>

192
00:10:55,696 --> 00:10:58,741
<b>[KYARA] Do you mind
screaming babies on the bus?</b>

193
00:11:00,577 --> 00:11:04,414
<b>Yeah, I think
they're annoying.</b>

194
00:11:06,833 --> 00:11:09,836
<b>[KYARA] Are your mom
and dad still alive?</b>

195
00:11:09,877 --> 00:11:11,379
<b>[groans]</b>

196
00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:14,174
<b>They are.</b>

197
00:11:14,215 --> 00:11:16,426
<b>[KYARA] Do you love them?</b>

198
00:11:16,468 --> 00:11:18,512
<b>♪ ♪</b>

199
00:11:18,553 --> 00:11:21,097
<b>[MOEGI] I'd like
to kill both of them.</b>

200
00:11:21,139 --> 00:11:24,892
<b>♪ ♪</b>

201
00:11:24,934 --> 00:11:26,436
<b>Oh?</b>

202
00:11:27,103 --> 00:11:34,444
<b>♪ ♪</b>

203
00:11:45,121 --> 00:11:48,500
<b>If you have any
questions, ask Shion.</b>

204
00:11:48,542 --> 00:11:49,876
<b>Uh, OK.</b>

205
00:12:05,559 --> 00:12:07,268
<b>[bag thuds]</b>

206
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:10,771
<b>[sighs]</b>

207
00:12:11,523 --> 00:12:14,234
<b>[crashing]</b>

208
00:12:14,984 --> 00:12:18,238
<b>[whirring]</b>

209
00:12:24,452 --> 00:12:26,663
<b>[groans]</b>

210
00:12:47,934 --> 00:12:49,519
<b>[MOEGI] Hi, Shion.</b>

211
00:12:52,105 --> 00:12:54,566
<b>I'm Moegi.</b>

212
00:12:54,608 --> 00:12:57,402
<b>It's, um, nice to meet you.</b>

213
00:13:01,948 --> 00:13:03,199
<b>[grumbles]</b>

214
00:13:03,950 --> 00:13:05,577
<b>[crash]</b>

215
00:13:08,204 --> 00:13:11,332
<b>Do you know what's
breaking all the glass?</b>

216
00:13:12,584 --> 00:13:15,712
<b>[crashing]</b>

217
00:13:16,795 --> 00:13:18,047
<b>Shut up!</b>

218
00:13:19,257 --> 00:13:22,009
<b>[whimpers]</b>

219
00:13:23,261 --> 00:13:25,012
<b>[grunts]</b>

220
00:13:25,764 --> 00:13:27,474
<b>[creaks]</b>

221
00:13:30,727 --> 00:13:34,481
<b>[whirring, thudding]</b>

222
00:13:37,692 --> 00:13:40,612
<b>[soft music]</b>

223
00:13:40,654 --> 00:13:47,118
<b>♪ ♪</b>

224
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:50,079
<b>[water running,
dishes clinking]</b>

225
00:13:50,121 --> 00:13:54,668
<b>♪ ♪</b>

226
00:13:54,709 --> 00:13:57,295
<b>[MOEGI] I think your clothes
are cute, Kyara.</b>

227
00:13:58,921 --> 00:14:00,340
<b>[KYARA] Do you?</b>

228
00:14:00,381 --> 00:14:01,466
<b>Yeah.</b>

229
00:14:01,508 --> 00:14:03,217
<b>Do you prefer loose clothing?</b>

230
00:14:03,259 --> 00:14:04,427
<b>[KYARA] I do.</b>

231
00:14:05,637 --> 00:14:08,640
<b>You'd look awesome
in something formfitting, too.</b>

232
00:14:08,682 --> 00:14:11,685
<b>You got the body for it,
not like me.</b>

233
00:14:11,726 --> 00:14:13,852
<b>♪ ♪</b>

234
00:14:13,894 --> 00:14:17,064
<b>[KYARA] I can't stand
wearing tight clothes.</b>

235
00:14:17,106 --> 00:14:18,899
<b>[gasps]</b>

236
00:14:19,651 --> 00:14:20,735
<b>Sorry.</b>

237
00:14:20,777 --> 00:14:22,612
<b>I didn't know.</b>

238
00:14:22,654 --> 00:14:29,952
<b>♪ ♪</b>

239
00:14:32,413 --> 00:14:33,665
<b>Hey.</b>

240
00:14:35,500 --> 00:14:38,127
<b>I feel like going out
and killing someone.</b>

